      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AGENT TWENTY ONE (2) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 22.87. Fair draw can see a good run and has the ability and in winning form. Is yet to taste defeat in three starts from this draw. Looks to have an edge on most of these. ALGORITHM (1) was narrowly beaten last time, jumping from this same box when a neck second in a Grade 6 over 531m at this track. Harder here but expected to feature again. COOL BLUE YOU (7) finds it hard to break through. Has hit the frame the last two runs, the latest when second (30.76) at Angle Park. Has a good record at this journey. Well placed and gets her chance. ZIPPING THERON (6) placed last time out at this track and distance - worth considering.",
